      "description": "The DF Tactical 30 ETF (DFTT) is an exchange-traded fund that is based on the DF Risk-Managed Tactical Top 30 index. The fund tracks an equally weighted index of the top 30 US large-cap stocks selected based on price momentum. Security selection uses a regularly monitored exponential moving average (EMA) DFTT was launched on Nov 11, 2025 and is issued by Donoghue Forlines.",
